divs: Sighting DetailsI saw tha object when I was 8 years old in 1995. I am 15 now. I dont rememberexactly what happened. But I remember I was siting on my bed looking out mybedroom window. It was very early in the morning...maybe one or 2 oclock. Ilooked towards the mountains and saw the object. It was there for a few minutesand then went straight up. I really didnt think much of it. After that I raninto my mothers room. She didnt see anything. And I had forgotten about ituntil about a year ago
Summary: Black disk, neon blue lights, rotating
